4.4.1 The Debug structure

infoAll

Function

Structure

Shell.Debug

Type

val infoAll: unit -> string list

Syntax

infoAll () -> strings

Arguments

()

Values

strings
A list of strings.

Description

Returns a printable representation of debugging information compiled for all functions. For internal use only.
